    "ROCKET has two extensions.",
    "The first extension is MiniROCKET (Dempster et al. 2021), which speeds up ROCKET by over an order of magnitude with no significant difference in accuracy.",
    "MiniROCKET removes many of the random components of ROCKET, making the classifier almost deterministic.",
    "The kernel length is fixed to 9, only two weight values are used, and the bias value is drawn from the convolution output.",
    "Only the PPV is extracted, discarding the max."
